## CLAUDE CODE SKILL

A Claude Code skill file is included to give Claude expert knowledge of
this package's API.  To install it, symlink the skill directory into your
Claude skills directory:

```sh
ln -s /path/to/@PACKAGE_NAME@/claude/skills/encoding-decoding-cbor ~/.claude/skills/encoding-decoding-cbor
```

Once installed, Claude Code will automatically use the skill when working
with CBOR data in Tcl.


